\begin_layout Standard
Energy momentum tensor:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)=-\frac{i}{8}\left[L_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)-L_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)\right]=-\frac{i}{2}P_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)\,.
\]

