\begin_layout Standard
Clover part of the action:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S\left(x\right)=\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)T\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset

where
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T\left(x\right)=\frac{c_{sw}}{2}\sum_{\mu\neq\nu}\sigma_{\mu\nu}F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)=2ic_{sw}\sum_{\mu<\nu}\gamma_{\mu}\gamma_{\nu}F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)=c_{sw}\sum_{\mu<\nu}\gamma_{\mu}\gamma_{\nu}P_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)\,,
\]

\end_inset

computed in the last part of 
